spec_data.Name: eclipse-recommenders
spec_data.Description:
Code Recommenders automatically analyzes existing code using APIs and extracts
common usage rules and patterns from it. In the form of recommendation models,
this knowledge is then fed back into your IDE. Code Recommenders’ intelligent
code completion and augmented API documentation then utilizes the power of
these models to provide you with the solutions implemented by other developers
in the past. This helps you to get up to speed with the new framework or API
without countless hours of searching the Internet for the solutions to common
problems.
